    <title>hexo主题next7.8版本美化</title>
    <url>/2021/06/26/hexo%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98next7-8%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="1-设置博主个人信息以及语言"><a href="#1-设置博主个人信息以及语言" class="headerlink" title="1.设置博主个人信息以及语言"></a>1.设置博主个人信息以及语言</h1><h3 id="1-1-在博客配置文件中修改Site"><a href="#1-1-在博客配置文件中修改Site" class="headerlink" title="1.1 在博客配置文件中修改Site"></a>1.1 在博客配置文件中修改Site</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">程序鱼</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">subtitle:</span> <span class="string">云飞</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">description:</span> <span class="string">因为热爱所以喜欢，因为喜欢所以坚持</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">keywords:</span> </span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">author:</span> <span class="string">codefishyyf</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">language:</span> <span class="string">zh-CN</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">timezone:</span> <span class="string">Asia/Shanghai</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="2-设置next主题，更改样式"><a href="#2-设置next主题，更改样式" class="headerlink" title="2.设置next主题，更改样式"></a>2.设置next主题，更改样式</h1><h3 id="2-1在博客配置文件中修改theme为next"><a href="#2-1在博客配置文件中修改theme为next" class="headerlink" title="2.1在博客配置文件中修改theme为next"></a>2.1在博客配置文件中修改theme为next</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">theme:</span> <span class="string">next</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="2-2在主题配置文件中选择一种样式"><a href="#2-2在主题配置文件中选择一种样式" class="headerlink" title="2.2在主题配置文件中选择一种样式"></a>2.2在主题配置文件中选择一种样式</h3><p>这个是我的样式，你们可以选择自己喜欢的样式【只要把前面的#去掉】</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Schemes</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#scheme: Muse</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#scheme: Mist</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#scheme: Pisces</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">scheme:</span> <span class="string">Gemini</span> </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="3-Menu增加标签、分类、关于页面"><a href="#3-Menu增加标签、分类、关于页面" class="headerlink" title="3. Menu增加标签、分类、关于页面"></a>3. Menu增加标签、分类、关于页面</h1><p>第一步：根据自己的需要，去掉对应功能前面的#号，</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">menu:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">home:</span> <span class="string">/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">home</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">about:</span> <span class="string">/about/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">user</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">tags:</span> <span class="string">/tags/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">tags</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">categories:</span> <span class="string">/categories/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">th</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">archives:</span> <span class="string">/archives/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">archive</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#schedule: /schedule/ || calendar</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#sitemap: /sitemap.xml || sitemap</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#commonweal: /404/ || heartbeat</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>第二步：新建这些页面</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">hexo</span> <span class="string">new</span> <span class="string">page</span> <span class="string">&quot;about&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">hexo</span> <span class="string">new</span> <span class="string">page</span> <span class="string">&quot;tags&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">hexo</span> <span class="string">new</span> <span class="string">page</span> <span class="string">&quot;categories&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>第三步：修改这些页面的配置</p>
<p>source\about\index.md</p>
<p>source\tags\index.md</p>
<p>source\categories\index.md</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">关于</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">&quot;about&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">标签</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">&quot;tags&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">分类</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">&quot;categories&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="4-添加搜索功能"><a href="#4-添加搜索功能" class="headerlink" title="4. 添加搜索功能"></a>4. 添加搜索功能</h1><h3 id="4-1-方式一"><a href="#4-1-方式一" class="headerlink" title="4.1 方式一"></a>4.1 方式一</h3><p>第一步：安装插件【我这里使用的是exo-generator-searchdb】</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">npm</span> <span class="string">install</span> <span class="string">hexo-generator-searchdb</span> <span class="string">--save</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>第二步：博客配置文件中添加并修改local_search</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">search:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">path:</span> <span class="string">search.xml</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">field:</span> <span class="string">post</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">format:</span> <span class="string">html</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">limit:</span> <span class="number">10000</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">local_search:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="4-2-方式二"><a href="#4-2-方式二" class="headerlink" title="4.2 方式二"></a>4.2 方式二</h3><p>修改主题配置文件中local_Search如下【推荐】</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Local Search</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">Dependencies:</span> <span class="string">https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-generator-searchdb</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">local_search:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="5-取消hexo文章目录对标题的自动编号"><a href="#5-取消hexo文章目录对标题的自动编号" class="headerlink" title="5.取消hexo文章目录对标题的自动编号"></a>5.取消hexo文章目录对标题的自动编号</h1><p> 将主题配置文件中的mumber 改成false</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">number:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="6-设置左上角或者右上角github图标"><a href="#6-设置左上角或者右上角github图标" class="headerlink" title="6.设置左上角或者右上角github图标"></a>6.设置左上角或者右上角github图标</h1><p>在主题配置文件中，启用github-banner</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">github_banner:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">permalink:</span> <span class="string">https://github.com/codefishyyf</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">Follow</span> <span class="string">me</span> <span class="string">on</span> <span class="string">GitHub</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="7-设置阅读进度百分比显示"><a href="#7-设置阅读进度百分比显示" class="headerlink" title="7.设置阅读进度百分比显示"></a>7.设置阅读进度百分比显示</h1><p>在博客配置文件下，修改back2top中的参数如下所示：</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">back2top:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">sidebar:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">scrollpercent:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="8-设置阅读位置标记功能"><a href="#8-设置阅读位置标记功能" class="headerlink" title="8.设置阅读位置标记功能"></a>8.设置阅读位置标记功能</h1><p>在主题配置文件下，设置如下：</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">bookmark:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Customize the color of the bookmark.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">color:</span> <span class="string">&quot;#222&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># If auto, save the reading progress when closing the page or clicking the bookmark-icon.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># If manual, only save it by clicking the bookmark-icon.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">save:</span> <span class="string">auto</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="9-设置统计字数和阅读时间的估计"><a href="#9-设置统计字数和阅读时间的估计" class="headerlink" title="9.设置统计字数和阅读时间的估计"></a>9.设置统计字数和阅读时间的估计</h1><p>在主题配置文件下，设置如下：</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">symbols_count_time:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">separated_meta:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">item_text_post:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">item_text_total:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="10-添加文章分享按钮"><a href="#10-添加文章分享按钮" class="headerlink" title="10.添加文章分享按钮"></a>10.添加文章分享按钮</h1><p>第一步：在next主题下的source/lib中安装needmoreshare2模块</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">git</span> <span class="string">clone</span> <span class="string">https://github.com/theme-next/theme-next-needmoreshare2</span> <span class="string">source/lib/needsharebutton</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>第二步：在主题配置文件中添加如下代码：</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#添加文章分享按钮模块</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">needmoreshare2:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">postbottom:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">options:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">iconStyle:</span> <span class="string">default</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">boxForm:</span> <span class="string">horizontal</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">position:</span> <span class="string">bottomCenter</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">networks:</span> <span class="string">Weibo,Wechat,Douban,QQZone</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">float:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">options:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">iconStyle:</span> <span class="string">default</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">boxForm:</span> <span class="string">horizontal</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">position:</span> <span class="string">middleRight</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">networks:</span> <span class="string">Weibo,Wechat,Douban,QQZone</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="11-添加自定义404页面"><a href="#11-添加自定义404页面" class="headerlink" title="11.添加自定义404页面"></a>11.添加自定义404页面</h1><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">暂时还没完成</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="12图片放大预览功能"><a href="#12图片放大预览功能" class="headerlink" title="12图片放大预览功能"></a>12图片放大预览功能</h1><p>在主题配置文件下启动fancybox</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">fancybox:true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="13图片懒加载"><a href="#13图片懒加载" class="headerlink" title="13图片懒加载"></a>13图片懒加载</h1><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">lazyload:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="14点击出现桃心效果"><a href="#14点击出现桃心效果" class="headerlink" title="14点击出现桃心效果"></a>14点击出现桃心效果</h1><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">暂时还没完成</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="15标签云效果"><a href="#15标签云效果" class="headerlink" title="15标签云效果"></a>15标签云效果</h1><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">暂时还没完成</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="16设置代码块复制和代码高亮"><a href="#16设置代码块复制和代码高亮" class="headerlink" title="16设置代码块复制和代码高亮"></a>16设置代码块复制和代码高亮</h1><p>在主题配置文件中修改codeblock</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">codeblock:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">highlight_theme:</span> <span class="string">normal</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">copy_button:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">show_result:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">style:</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="17修改文章底部标签样式"><a href="#17修改文章底部标签样式" class="headerlink" title="17修改文章底部标签样式"></a>17修改文章底部标签样式</h1><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">tag_icon:true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



